{"id": "1180308457124003860", "channel_id": "1180308457124003860", "type": 0, "author_id": "803234818795241513", "author_name": "may_una", "author_bot": false, "content": "法洛絲抽牌丟給朵爾等價補血\n一路一直盾靠凱刻斯反擊+觸手打\n分反正無腦盾就好，珊的狂氣也能拿盾打人\n\n我都直接移除打擊卡了w", "timestamp": "2023-12-02T00:44:25.249000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1180308457316958228", "filename": "Screenshot_2023-12-02-01-20-07-37_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 141344, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1180308457124003860/1180308457316958228/Screenshot_2023-12-02-01-20-07-37_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg?ex=69ff2c29&is=69fddaa9&hm=bed297c177e058302aa29cb69b3e1894c39518074d5a179b800d0faf748a9c08&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1180308457124003860", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "無腦一直盾", "forum_channel_id": "1180087318506393630", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1183747314607730688"]}
